Trade/Device Name(s): OMNis Health Embrace Glucose Control Solution
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): OMNis Health Embrace blood glucose test systems
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for OMNis Health Embrace Glucose Control Solution as a control material for verifying OMNis Health Embrace blood glucose test system performance
Indications for Use Summary: Intended to assess performance of OMNis Health Embrace blood glucose test systems for use by healthcare professionals and people with diabetes mellitus at home
